desc: Holistic Wellness services such as Massage Therapy, Psychotherapy, Reiki, Arvigo, Energy Healing, Psychic Readings. A brick and mortar as well as online boutique featuring: fair trade gifts, crystals, soy wax candles, CBD, handmade jewelry, local artists, black owned, women owned business.

layout.text:
The Healing Collective NY is Westchester County's Premier Destination for Healing and Personal Transformation.
Our Holistic Wellness Experts are here to provide you with the highest quality services in their field.
Massage Therapy, Health Coaching, Energy Healing, Reiki, Acupuncture, Holistic Psychotherapy, Nutritional Counseling, Intuitive Coaching, Psychic Readings and more.
Make sure to stop in to our crystal boutique on the street level where you'll find a variety of products to support your most vibrant health as well as fair trade, locally made, women owned and black owned vendors highlighted.
